def generate_permutations(S):
    ip = S[1:]
    op = S[1]
    ans = []

    def solve(ip, op):
        if len(ip) == 0:
            ans.append(op)
            return
        op1 = op + ip[0]
        op2 = op + ' ' + ip[0]
        ip = ip[1:]
        solve(ip, op1)
        solve(ip, op2)
    solve(ip, op)
    return sorted(ans)
